[215.823978, "o", "Stacking 5 bowls with dy=2:\r\n  Bowl 1 at dy=0: OK\r\n  Bowl 2 at dy=2: OK\r\n  Bowl 3 at dy=4: OK\r\n  Bowl 4 at dy=6: OK\r\n  Bowl 5 at dy=8: OK\r\n\r\nCombined: 90 cells, bbox=12x12\r\nIn 3D with z=6: bbox=12x12x6 = 864\r\n\r\nCombined layout:\r\n  y= 0: ##........##  bowls: 1\r\n  y= 1: .##......##.  bowls: 1\r\n  y= 2: ####....####  bowls: 1,2\r\n  y= 3: .##########.  bowls: 1,2\r\n  y= 4: ####....####  bowls: 2,3\r\n  y= 5: .##########.  bowls: 2,3\r\n  y= 6: ####....####  bowls: 3,4\r\n  y= 7: .##########.  bowls: 3,4\r\n  y= 8: ####....####  bowls: 4,5\r\n  y= 9: .##########.  bowls: 4,5\r\n  y=10: ..##....##..  bowls: 5\r\n  y=11: ...######...  bowls: 5\r\n\r\nEmpty cells in bbox: 54\r\nFill ratio: 90/144 = 62.50%\r\n\r\n\r\nStacking 5 bowls with dy=1:\r\n  Bowl 1 at dy=0: OK\r\n  Bowl 2 at dy=1: OVERLAP of 6 cells!\r\n"]
